 
<p>
The fanatical Christians that is the Texas Republican Party plan to
require display of
<a href="https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2023/apr/21/texas-classrooms-ten-commandments-bill">a religious statement in every classroom</a>.
<p>
This would directly defy the First Amendment, which bans establishment
of religion.
<p>
In normal times, we would confidently expect federal courts to quash
this &mdash; but no one can be sure nowadays.

